{"tid":1882804,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"欅坂46暨日向坂46交流區第九十回 有新人係咪有九單","createTime":"2020-02-16T13:12:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-17T02:59:42.000Z","uid":309384,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ba6e34242b1f4bcaab79cf5e99ac708a0d25c84b","tid":1882804,"uid":309384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:12:29.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">  </span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EkfrB5y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEkfrB5y.gif&h=3c9b3390&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/kIW7mlj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FkIW7mlj.gif&h=95dc42fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/jX7n78H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FjX7n78H.gif&h=703830aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/xvQJaUW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FxvQJaUW.gif&h=f3eb09e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/020230_b9331b514fb885b933e889c2825caf75.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F020230_b9331b514fb885b933e889c2825caf75.gif&h=e7566900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CR9WZiG.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCR9WZiG.gif&h=cdc94b38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yX1vsNI.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FyX1vsNI.gif&h=40821bca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/cttWDoFhUiiWqL6d7f/giphy.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.giphy.com%2Fmedia%2FcttWDoFhUiiWqL6d7f%2Fgiphy.gif&h=2d3ff6a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CsAtFb6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCsAtFb6.gif&h=4124a921&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mxKutLO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmxKutLO.gif&h=1e818df4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dkjm7dT.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdkjm7dT.gif&h=43cebbdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Eat1qYW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEat1qYW.gif&h=7c2262d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gAp5L0N.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgAp5L0N.gif&h=5eb0c9de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">欅坂46(Keyakizaka46)是日本大型女子偶像組合乃木坂46的姐妹組合</span>，製作人同樣為秋元康。組合名字中的「46」讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而不是讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。2016年4月6日，欅坂46出道單曲《サイレントマジョリティー》販售，首週銷量達261,580枚，除了登上Oricon週榜首位，還同時刷新當時歷代女性藝人銷量最高的出道單曲。2016年12月31日，出道不足一年即登場NHK紅白歌合戰。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://www.keyakizaka46.com/img/14/diar/88/mem/member/sub-member-6897_jpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.keyakizaka46.com%2Fimg%2F14%2Fdiar%2F88%2Fmem%2Fmember%2Fsub-member-6897_jpg.jpg&h=c3ef22e5&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n日向坂46（Hinatazaka46）是日本大型女子偶像團體，與乃木坂46、櫸坂46、吉本坂46同為坂道系列團體之一。團體名稱的「46」與坂道系列其他團體同樣採用英文讀作「Forty-six／フォーティシックス」，而非讀作「四十六／よんじゅうろく」。成立於2015年11月29日，原名為平假名欅坂46（けやき坂46）。起源是由於營運為了給予以特例加入欅坂46的長濱ねる在團內適當的名份而創立，當時定位為欅坂46旗下的分團。2019年2月11日自欅坂46獨立，並改為現名，成為坂道系列第4個系列團體。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://cdn.keyakizaka46.com/files/14/diary/k46/member/moblog/201807/mob4wEGI2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn.keyakizaka46.com%2Ffiles%2F14%2Fdiary%2Fk46%2Fmember%2Fmoblog%2F201807%2Fmob4wEGI2.jpg&h=801bf1a6&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">成員名單</span></span><br />\n欅坂46<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMGtH2L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMGtH2L.jpg&h=9562f665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bw19suq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBw19suq.jpg&h=29f5dba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n欅坂46 2期生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/htv10w1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhtv10w1.jpg&h=07b2fcda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日向坂46<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jNheMbW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjNheMbW.png&h=784d8b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日向坂46 2期生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OgDYtqi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOgDYtqi.png&h=abc6050d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日向坂46 3期生<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dRbvjwZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdRbvjwZ.png&h=909b8142&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/he1D04c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhe1D04c.jpg&h=55b1e832&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ChbgNKf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FChbgNKf.jpg&h=4b201d18&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">欅坂46 LIVE at 東京ドーム ～ARENA TOUR 2019 FINAL～」DVD/Blu-ray好評発売中!!!</span></span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://cdn.hinatazaka46.com/files/14/hinata/pages/3rd_single_sp/img/kv/kv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hinatazaka46.com%2Ffiles%2F14%2Fhinata%2Fpages%2F3rd_single_sp%2Fimg%2Fkv%2Fkv.jpg&h=bd866532&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">日向坂46 3rdシングル『こんなに好きになっちゃっていいの？』好評発売中!!!</span></span></div><br />\n[center]<br />\n【成員有幾靚女？】我直接用例子答你。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QZH7UpB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQZH7UpB.jpg&h=2f771bbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OM7S5wh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOM7S5wh.jpg&h=20c93eca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aDFM9XY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaDFM9XY.jpg&h=ecdfc533&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9423a526821619f2b49b70fa12bf33c9bd847262","tid":1882804,"uid":309384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:13:29.000Z","msg":"頂 點解嗰template cut咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7475c365eabed348d0a0ec247287299e278872a","tid":1882804,"uid":309384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:14:34.000Z","msg":"有冇大佬幫手開過個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be2adcb55345ef2ab2b8013ae8f47ac296538ef0","tid":1882804,"uid":34304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:20:57.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"462d8ae8e5eebea94ce60897276e6c6425ea9552","tid":1882804,"uid":146579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7475c365eabed348d0a0ec247287299e278872a","tid":1882804,"uid":309384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:14:34.000Z","msg":"有冇大佬幫手開過個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:24:12.000Z","msg":"你Q&amp;A到template個度就得 唔洗再開啦"},{"pid":"20cdb378cd3468d96c7ffd339002106ca424e300","tid":1882804,"uid":146579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:24:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>有冇大佬幫手開過個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>你補返Q&amp;A到template個度就得 唔洗再開啦</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1af8dfa13a16c3cfb407c52525d79b350b102d06","tid":1882804,"uid":127583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:31:02.000Z","msg":"@鈴本美愉 ： template已update 照copy template link即可"},{"pid":"4513a9eb8891de95671874fa1dc3fb8a66ef27e1","tid":1882804,"uid":309384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-16T13:31:19.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">歡迎新人加入</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/keyakizaka46sort.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fkeyakizaka46style.com%2Fsort%2Fkeyakizaka46sort.html&d=sh6QB3P1ZXxG4EHsBexfbmWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=93ea8157\" target=\"_blank\">http://keyakizaka46style.com/sort/keyakizaka46sort.html</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請新/舊手足定期體檢，以便加入DD黨</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">Q&amp;A</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n1）欅坂46/日向坂46乃何許人也？ <br />\n簡單來說，欅坂46/日向坂46是來自日本的偶像組合，演戲唱歌跳舞等全部都會參與，是正統全能型偶像。 <br />\n<br />\n2）那裡可以購買欅坂46/日向坂46既有關產品（生寫、CD、海報、寫真集、演唱會等）？ <br />\n一般來說，信和地庫會有存貨，不過價錢就...另外有不少商品需於官方WEBSHOP/會場購入，不過這裡有機會提供代購，要看看手足們的心情。 <br />\n<br />\n3）這裡可否討論欅坂46/日向坂46以外的組合？ <br />\n可以。但皆因這裡主要討論欅坂46/日向坂46，你可以理性討論、攻擊、黑其他成員(禾ru除外)，但講之前請先作好世界大戰的準備。所以勸喻各位尊重member，尊重手足。<br />\n<br />\n4）那麼我要如何見到欅坂46/日向坂46成員？ <br />\n握手會，演唱會...etc，詳細請問手足<br />\n<br />\n5）呢度大佬係? <br />\n連登會員平手友梨奈<br />\n<br />\n6）高登會然橋本奈奈未/連登會然舞木香純是咪HIHI？<br />\n是。因為三槍為人臭串、極度無恥，自然會引起其他手足責罵他。雖然佢犯禁逼走不少手足，但因他臉皮極厚，罵極不走真是無可奈何。 <br />\n<br />\n7）點睇響呢套戲？<br />\n必睇指數10粒星<br />\n<br />\n8）有人黎搞事挑戰咁點算?<br />\n對付戇尻仔既最好方法就係無視佢。眼不見為淨既野，相信大家都明架喇。你有興趣同佢嘈既話你可以繼續，但相信大家都唔會想浪費時間係啲戇尻仔身上。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"col